<h1>认</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">rèn</span><span class=alesi>(ren4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 认 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 认</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/recognize" style="color:black;">recognize</a>, <a href="/dictionary/know" style="color:black;">know</a>, <a href="/dictionary/understand" style="color:black;">understand</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 4<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 4 strokes: <a href="/character/不" title="bu4: no, not; un-; negative prefix">不</a>, <a href="/character/中" title="zhong1: central; center, middle; in the midst of; hit (target); attain">中</a>, <a href="/character/为" title="wei4: do, handle, govern, act; be">为</a>, <a href="/character/以" title="yi3: by means of; thereby, therefore; consider as; in order to">以</a>, <a href="/character/方" title="fang1: a square, rectangle; a region; local">方</a>, <a href="/character/天" title="tian1: sky, heaven; god, celestial">天</a>, <a href="/character/分" title="fen1: divide; small unit of time etc.">分</a>, <a href="/character/心" title="xin1: heart; mind, intelligence; soul">心</a>, <a href="/character/开" title="kai1: open; initiate, begin, start">开</a>, <a href="/character/从" title="cong2: from, by, since, whence, through">从</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/言" title="Kangxi radical 149">言</a>&nbsp;149.2</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 1 <br><small>Other HSK 1 characters: <a href="/character/几" title="ji3: small table">几</a>, <a href="/character/系" title="xi4: system; line, link, connection">系</a>, <a href="/character/气" title="qi4: steam, vapor; KangXi radical 84">气</a>, <a href="/character/名" title="ming2: name, rank, title, position">名</a>, <a href="/character/打" title="da3: strike, hit, beat; fight; attack">打</a>, <a href="/character/女" title="nü3: woman, girl; feminine; rad. 38">女</a>, <a href="/character/水" title="shui3: water, liquid, lotion, juice">水</a>, <a href="/character/四" title="si4: four">四</a>, <a href="/character/电" title="dian4: electricity; electric; lightning">电</a>, <a href="/character/东" title="dong1: east, eastern, eastward">东</a> <a href="/cha